rectors-movies-full-list-1201348569/|title=DGA Awards Film Nominations: Anderson, Eastwood, Inarritu, Linklater, Tyldum|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=January 13, 2015|accessdate=January 13, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Empire Awards]]\n| [[Empire Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]]\n| Bradley Cooper\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.empireonline.com/awards2015/|title=Vote Now For The Jameson Empire Awards 2015|work=empireonline.com}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Iowa Film Critics\n| Best Movie Yet to Open in Iowa\n| ''American Sniper'' <small>(tied with ''[[A Most Violent Year]]'')\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/boyhood-is-iowa-critics-best-picture-of-2014|title='Boyhood' is Iowa Critics' Best Picture of 2014|publisher=Hitfix|date=January 7, 2015|accessdate=January 9, 2015}}</ref> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| [[Motion Picture Sound Editors|MPSE Golden Reel Awards]]\n| Feature English Language - Effects/Foley\n| Bub Asman, Alan Robert Murray\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=https://deadline.com/2015/01/birdman-dawn-of-the-planet-of-the-apes-motion-picture-sound-editor-awards-nominations-1201350012/|title='Birdman', 'Apes' Top 2015 Golden Reel Nominations|website=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=January 14, 2015|accessdate=January 14, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=row rowspan=\"2\"| [[MTV Movie Awards]]\n| Movie of the Year\n| ''American Sniper''\n| {{nom}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2095540/mtv-movie-awards-nominations-2015/|title=Here Are Your 2015 MTV Movie Awards Nominees|work=MTV News}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Male Performance\n| Bradley Cooper\n| {{won}}\n|-\n! scope=row rowspan=\"2\"| [[National Board of Review]]\n| [[National Board of Review: Top Ten Films|Top Ten Film]]\n|\n| {{won}}\n| style=\"text-align:center;\" rowspan=\"2\"|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nationalboa